data.title: WARNING SHOT
data.meta_description: Status Quo - Warning shot (Letra y canción para escuchar) - Ticket to the world, learn a trade or two / Hey now, it suits me somehow / How 'bout you / Freeze me in the wind, burn me in the sun / Hey ho, on with the

Victory

Hey guys, try it for size

This ball and chain
